Is it time for a Rails upgrade?

Need ruby 2.2.2 for Rails


New methods in activerecord:

OR 
 - allows oyu to query for 2 things at the same time
 - if something is 1 OR 2 return 
 
BELONGS_TO 

attribute api - allows you to incorporate any api into rails upon rails new

has_secure_token : give the user a secure token (great for reset passwords, etc). 

Websockets: come inbuilt into rails, action cable 

- a way to set up a pipe between your clients ans server. Sets up an unlimited pipe between the client and server
- server pushed data to the client side automatically (w/o refreshing the page)


